@database TextClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - Text Class"


Text class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "AreaClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Text class is used to create text areas.

  See
  @{"Button()" LINK "Functions.guide/Button"}
  @{"ToggleButton()" LINK "Functions.guide/ToggleButton"}
  @{"Label()" LINK "Functions.guide/Label"}
  @{"Text()" LINK "Functions.guide/Text"}

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}Contents@{fg text}
  S I
  Use ParseText() to parse text

  @{fg shine}HiChar@{fg text}
  S I
  A char to be underlined.

  @{fg shine}HiCharIdx@{fg text}
  C I
  Underline the char that follows this (usually _)

  @{fg shine}Integer@{fg text}
  N ISGN
  You may use it to handle with an integral value rather than a
  string

  @{fg shine}Preparse@{fg text}
  S IS

  @{fg shine}SetMax@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}SetMin@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}SetVMax@{fg text}
  B I

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  None defined

@EndNode

